@startuml
[*] --> Start
Start --> Running: [*]
Running --> CollectingData: ClockTriggered
CollectingData --> Running: DataCollected
Running --> PreparingSummary: SummaryRequested
PreparingSummary --> Running: SummaryPrepared
Running --> CheckingStatus: StatusChecked
CheckingStatus --> Running: StatusTransmitted
Running --> ControlledMode: RemoteControlled
ControlledMode --> ShutDown: ShutdownCommand
ShutDown --> Start: Restarted
@enduml
